com.vectorprint.configuration.decoration

Class AbstractPropertiesDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vectorprint.configuration.decoration.AbstractPropertiesDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EnhancedMap, Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,String[]>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CachingProperties, FindableProperties, HelpSupportedProperties, ObservableProperties, ParsingProperties, PreparingProperties, ReadonlyProperties, ThreadSafeProperties

    public abstract class AbstractPropertiesDecorator
extends Object
implements EnhancedMap
    Base class for all decorators that add functionality to Settings. All implemented methods just call the embedded EnhancedMap.
    Author:
    Eduard Drenth at VectorPrint.nl
